\id 2TH Kapingamarangi
\h 2 Thessalonians
\toc1 Di Lua Lede a Paul ang gi di Nohongo Dabu i Thessalonica
\toc2 2 Thessalonians
\toc3 2-Thessalonians
\mt1 2 THESSALONIANS
\mt2 Di Lua Lede a Paul ang gi di Nohongo Dabu i Thessalonica
\imt1 Di haga modongoohia:
\im Tee donu gi di lua hanimoi o Christ le e hana hua i golo i lodo di nohongo dabu i Thessalonica, gu haga hinihini nia daangada.
\ip \bk Di lua lede a Paul ang gi di Nohongo Dabu i Thessalonica\bk* le e helekai i di hagadonu o nia daangada o di nohongo dabu, ala e hai bolo di laangi dela e hanimoi ai Christ la guu lawa di hanimoi. Paul gu hagadonu gii donu di maanadu deenei, bolo i mua di lua hanimoi o Christ, gei nia huaidu o nia daangada, la koia ga huaidu huoloo, e dagi go tangada dela e haga ingoo bolo “Di Hagadaumee o God”, dela e hai baahi gi Christ.
\ip Paul e agoago maaloo ang gi di nohongo dabu i Thessalonica bolo digaula gi mau dangihi gi nadau hagadonu, ma e aha maa digaula gaa tale gi nia haingadaa be nia hagaduadua. Digaula gi hai hegau hua be Paul mo ono ehoo gau hai hegau, digaula gi daudali hua beelaa nadau hegau humalia.
\iot Di hagahonu di beebaa deenei:
\io1 Di haga modongoohia \ior (1.1-2)\ior*
\io1 Di hagaamu mo nia haga modongoohia \ior (1.3-12)\ior*
\io1 Di haga modongoohia di hanimoi o Christ \ior (2.1-17)\ior*
\io1 Di aago di hai o di mouli o nia dama a Christ \ior (3.1-15)\ior*
\io1 Di hagaodi di lede deenei \ior (3.16-18)\ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Mai baahi o Paul, Silas, mo Timothy, ang gi di nohongo dabu i Thessalonica, dela gu hai mee ginai tadau Damana go God, mo tadau Dagi go Jesus Christ:\x * \xo 1.1 \xt Acts 17.1\x*
\p 
\v 2 God Tamana mo tadau Dagi go Jesus Christ gi gowadu gi goodou tumaalia mo di noho i di aumaalia.
\s1 Di hagi aga i di hanimoi o Christ
\p 
\v 3 Madau duaahina nei, gimaadou e hai loo gi danggee gi God i nia madagoaa huogodoo i goodou. E donu belee hai go gimaadou beelaa, idimaa, godou hagadonu mo hagadau aaloho la gu tomo aga.
\v 4 Deelaa di mee e hagaamu ai goodou go gimaadou i lodo nia nohongo dabu a God. Gimaadou e hagaamu godou manawa hagakono, hagadonu, mo hagaduadua mono haga mmaemmae huogodoo ala ne tale adu gi goodou.
\p 
\v 5 Nia mee huogodoo aanei, le e haga modongoohia bolo di hagi aga a God le e donu, idimaa, di hagaodi gi muli o nia mee aanei, gei goodou gaa tau di ulu i Teenua King o God, dela e duadua ginai goodou.
\v 6 God gaa hai laa di mee dela e donu, e hagaduadua digau ala e hagaduadua goodou.
\v 7 Mee ga haga dagaloaha goodou ala e noho i lodo nia hagaduadua, mo gimaadou. Mee gaa hai di mee deenei i di madagoaa Jesus ma ga haneia i di langi mo\f + \fr 1.7 \ft \bk mo\bk* be: \bk madalia\bk*\f* ana gau di langi maaloo dangihi,
\v 8 mo di ulaula di ahi, e hagaduadua digau ala e haga de iloo a God, mo digau ala hagalee daudali di Longo Humalia o tadau Dagi Jesus.
\v 9 Digaula ga hagaduadua gi di hagaduadua e dee odi, gaa wwae gi daha mo Tagi mo nia madamada ono mahi,\x * \xo 1.9 \xt Isaiah 2.10\x*
\v 10 i di laangi ma ga hanimoi iei Mee belee hagamadamada go ana daangada huogodoo, mo di hagalaamua go digau huogodoo ala gu hagadonu. Goodou ga madalia digaula, idimaa, goodou gu hagadonu madau helekai ala ne hagi adu gi goodou.
\p 
\v 11 Deelaa di mee e dalodalo ai gimaadou i nia madagoaa huogodoo i goodou. Gimaadou e dangi ang gi God gi haga dohu ina goodou ang gi dono mouli dela ne gahi ginai goodou gi mouli ai. God gi heia goodou gii mee di haga kila aga godou hiihai humalia mai i ono mahi, ge gi hagangudu ina gi muli godou hegau i di hagadonu.
\v 12 Deenei di godou hai e haga madamada ai di ingoo o tadau Dagi go Jesus, gei Mee e haga madamada labelaa goodou, mai i tumaalia o tadau God mo tadau Dagi go Jesus Christ.
\c 2
\s1 Tangada hai mee hala
\p 
\v 1 Ogu duaahina nei, di hai o di hanimoi o tadau Dagi go Jesus Christ, mo tadau dagabuli mai gi dono baahi: au e dangi adu gi goodou bolo\x * \xo 2.1 \xt 1-Thessalonians 4.15-17\x*
\v 2 hudee hagahinihini ina godou hagabaubau be manawa gee gi nia helekai ala e hai bolo di Laangi o Tagi la gu dau mai. Holongo hunu daangada e hagamaanadu bolo ma nia helekai ni gimaadou ne hai i lodo madau agoago be madau hagadele nnelekai a God, be ne hihi i lodo di lede.
\v 3 Goodou hudee dumaalia gi nia daangada gi halahalau ina goodou gi nia helekai beenei, idimaa, di laangi deelaa la hagalee dau mai gaa dae loo gi di hai baahi haga muliagina gaa hai, mo di gila aga tangada hai mee hala dela belee hudu gi lodo di gowaa hagaduadua.
\v 4 Mee ga hai baahi gi nia mee huogodoo ala e hagaingoo bolo nia god ala e daumaha ginai nia daangada, mo nia mee huogodoo ala e dugu go nia daangada bolo nia mee haga madagu. Mee gaa bida haga menege aga ia gi hongo nia mee huogodoo, gaa hana ga ulu gi lodo di Hale Daumaha o God, gaa noho i golo, gaa hai bolo ia di God.\x * \xo 2.4 \xt Daniel 11.36; Ezekiel 28.2\x*
\p 
\v 5 Goodou gu de langahia? Au gu hagi adu di mee deenei i dogu madagoaa nogo i godou baahi.
\v 6 Ma di mee i golo dela e duuli di mee deenei bolo gi de gila aga dolomeenei. Goodou e iloo hua be di maa di aha. Malaa, dono madagoaa humalia, gei di Hagadaumee o God ga gila mai laa.
\v 7 Nia huaidu ala e nngala le e ngalua dolomeenei, gei di mee dela bolo e hai gii hai, ga hagalee hai, gaa dae loo gi di madagoaa o tangada dela e duuli di mee deelaa, la ga daa gi daha.
\v 8 Deelaa di madagoaa o tangada hai hala ga gila mai, malaa, Tagi Jesus ga hanimoi ga daaligi a mee gi nia madangi mai i dono ngudu, ga oho a mee gi nia gaagaa o dono hanimoi.\x * \xo 2.8 \xt Isaiah 11.4\x*
\v 9 Tangada hai hala ga hanimoi mo nia mogobuna o Setan, gaa hai ana hagadilinga mogobuna huogodoo mono mee haga goboina tilikai,\x * \xo 2.9 \xt Matthew 24.24\x*
\v 10 ga hai hegau i nia hagadilinga mee huaidu huogodoo belee halahalau digau ala belee kili gi daha. Digaula gaa kili gi daha, idimaa, digaula digi hai mee gi di tonu mo di aloho, bolo gi mouli ginaadou.
\v 11 Deenei laa, God ga hagau mai dana mogobuna haga hinihini e hagangalua nadau lodo bolo gi hagadonu digaula nia mee ala e hala.
\v 12 Malaa, di hagaodi gi muli o digau huogodoo ala hagalee hagadonu di mee dela e donu, ge tenetene gi di huaidu, la go di hagahuaidu.
\s1 Goodou ne hilihili ang gi di hagamouli
\p 
\v 13 Madau duaahina nei, gimaadou e hai loo gi danggee ang gi God i nia madagoaa huogodoo i goodou go digau ala e aloho ai di Tagi, idimaa, God ne hilihili goodou belee haga mouli matagidagi mai i di mogobuna o di Hagataalunga belee hai goodou gi dabuaahia, mo mai i godou hagadonu di tonu.
\v 14 God ne gahigahi mai goodou gi lodo tumaalia deenei mai i di Longo Humalia dela ne agoago go gimaadou adu gi goodou. Mee ne gahi mai goodou bolo gi hai mee gi di madamada o tadau Dagi go Jesus Christ.
\p 
\v 15 Madau duaahina nei, tuu gii mau ge gi daahia nia donu ala gu agoago adu go gimaadou mo i lodo di madau lede.
\p 
\v 16 Tadau Dagi go Jesus Christ, mo tadau Damana go God e aloho i gidaadou, e gaamai di manawa maaloo e noho hua beelaa mo di hagadagadagagee maaloo,
\v 17 gi haga maaloo ina aga goodou gii mahi, gii mee goodou di leelee mo di hai nia mee humalia i nia madagoaa huogodoo.
\c 3
\s1 Dalodalo i gimaadou
\p 
\v 1 Madau duaahina nei, dalodalo i gimaadou, bolo madau helekai mai baahi o tadau Dagi la gii dele limalima, gei nia daangada gi hagalabagau ina nnelekai aanei, gadoo be di dele nnelekai i godou baahi.
\v 2 Dalodalo ina labelaa gi God gi daawa gimaadou gi daha mo digau huaidu, idimaa, digau huogodoo la digi hagadonu nia helekai aalaa.
\p 
\v 3 Dimaadua le e manawa dahi, gei e hagamaaloo ge e abaaba goodou gi daha mo Tangada Huaidu deelaa.
\v 4 Gimaadou di madau hagadagadagagee mai baahi Dimaadua bolo goodou e hagamahi, e hai madau mee ala ne agoago adu gi goodou, gei ga duudagi hua beelaa gi muli.
\v 5 Tagi gi heia goodou gi iloo di aloho o God, ge gi hagamahi gii kae di manawa hagakono dela ne dugu mai go Christ.
\s1 Tuhongo hegau
\p 
\v 6 Madau duaahina nei, gimaadou e hagi ngudu adu i di ingoo o tadau Dagi go Jesus Christ, bolo hudee buni anga gi nia duaahina daumaha huogodoo ala e hagatoo ge hagalee daudali madau agoago.
\v 7 Goodou gu iloo humalia di godou mee belee hai, e daudali madau hangaahai. Gimaadou hagalee nogo hagatoo i godou baahi.
\v 8 Gimaadou digi kae nia hagamaamaa mai dahi dangada, maa digi huia. Gei gimaadou e ngalua i di boo mo di aa, bolo gi de haga daamaha tei dangada i goodou.
\v 9 Gimaadou ne hai beenei, hagalee bolo madau donu ai e kae madau hagamaamaa mai i godou baahi, gimaadou ne hai di ala mee belee daudali go goodou.
\v 10 Di madau madagoaa nogo noho i godou baahi, gimaadou gu helekai adu, “Tangada dela hagalee hiihai e ngalua, geia hudee miami.”
\p 
\v 11 Gimaadou e helekai beenei, idimaa, gimaadou gu longono bolo ma nia daangada i godou baahi e nohonoho hua balumee, nadau mee e hai ai, e haga deaadee nia moomee nia daangada.
\v 12 Gimaadou e helekai gi digau aanei i di ingoo o tadau Dagi go Jesus Christ, bolo gi ngalua, e hagahumalia ginaadou.
\p 
\v 13 Gei goodou, go madau duaahina, hudee buhi di hai nia mee ala e humalia.
\v 14 Holongo tangada i golo i godou baahi e hagalee daudali nia haganoho aanei ala ne hihi adu go gimaadou i lodo di madau lede deenei. Maa tangada beenei i golo, gei goodou hagailongo ina, hudee buni anga gi mee, gei mee ga langaadia.
\v 15 Hudee heia a mee bolo di hagadaumee ni goodou. Aago ina a mee be tuaahina daumaha ni goodou.
\s1 Nnelekai haga muliagina
\p 
\v 16 Tagi la go taamada o di aumaalia, gi gowadu gi goodou di noho i di aumaalia i nia madagoaa huogodoo mo i nia ala huogodoo. Tagi gii noho i godou baahi huogodoo.
\p 
\v 17 Au go Paul e hihi gi dogu lima donu boloo: \sig Taga aloho mai baahi o Paul\sig* Deenei dagu hai e haga ingoo agu lede huogodoo, deenei dagu hai e hihi agu mee.
\p 
\v 18 Tumaalia o tadau Dagi go Jesus Christ gi madalia goodou huogodoo. 
